  "description": {
    "zh": "你知道么，兄弟，我跟你说，针头线脑总是有价值的。不管在没在打仗，人们还是会买这些的。Ultra有很多品牌店，曾经被大家疯狂追捧的，我觉得我可以借用一下那儿的东西。去那里快速搜一圈，看看还是不是还有没被席卷一空的。记住不要搞些垃圾货色回来，我这儿只要名牌货。",
    "en": "You know, brother, I'll tell you what, clothes will always be of value. War or no war, people still buy that stuff. Ultra had a bunch of brand outlets, the ones folks used to hype on, and I could use the things from there now. Do a quick sweep, check if there is anything left if they’re not thrashed yet. Don't worry, I'm not asking you to loot any clothes, I just want you to check if there's anything left in the stores, we will figure everything out later. Just don’t go about rummaging through trash, remember, brand stuff only."
  },
